{"ts":"2026-06-27T18:34:13.404Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"submit_and_exit","toolCallId":"qxew9uvt","input":{"summary":"Connected both the Admin Documents page (app/admin/documents/page.tsx) and the Admin Billing/Invoices page (app/admin/billing/page.tsx) to their respective backend CRUD endpoints (/api/v1/documents and /api/v1/invoices).\n\nSpecifically:\n1. Admin Documents Page Integration:\n   - Synchronized the document grid/list view with the secure API v1 GET /api/v1/documents endpoint.\n   - Wired up document project assignment updates via PATCH /api/v1/documents/[id].\n   - Integrated zero-trust governance checklist status syncing using PATCH /api/v1/documents/[id].\n   - Connected document registration and HSM uploads to the API v1 POST /api/v1/documents endpoint.\n   - Connected document deprovisioning/deletion to DELETE /api/v1/documents/[id].\n\n2. Admin Billing Page Integration:\n   - Connected the admin invoice board to fetch all active billing records from GET /api/v1/invoices.\n   - Hooked up new invoice generation, which triggers a multi-step HSM ECC-256 cryptographic sealing simulation and writes directly to POST /api/v1/invoices.\n   - Connected invoice payment settlements and status updates to PATCH /api/v1/invoices/[id].\n   - Wired up ledger block archiving and deletion to DELETE /api/v1/invoices/[id].\n\nTested and validated all 9 API test suites (projects, AI operations, support, dashboard, analytics, users, governance, documents, and invoices) and verified they pass flawlessly with zero TypeScript or ESLint errors.","verified":true}}}
